nfident in their abilities and lets them \'own\' their own process.\"\r\n\r\n\"After having my children enrolled in Kumon for two years, I have come to the conclusion that all kids should do Kumon from the earliest age possible. The benefits are so great that no parent should have any doubts about enrolling his/her children in Kumon when they are still young.\"\r\n\r\nTo read more success stories from centres all over North America, visit<a href=\"http://www.Facebook.com/Kumon\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.Facebook.com/Kumon</a>','Twins!','','publish','closed','closed','','test-testimonials','','','2015-09-22 14:16:23','2015-09-22 14:16:23','',0,'http://1pixeldesign.com/dev/wordpress2/?post_type=onepix_testimonial&#038;p=530',0,'onepix_testimonial','',0),(531,1,'2014-02-18 03:42:55','2014-02-18 03:42:55','<strong>Amr, Mohamed, and Mariam\'s Story:</strong>\r\n\r\nThough they have only been in the Math and Reading programs for a relatively short time, especially Amr and Mohamed who have only been studying Reading since January of this year, both the twins and Mariam have become very advanced in the Math program, and are making steady progress in Reading.\r\n\r\nTheir mother, Abeer, is very enthusiastic about what they have gained through Kumon. She originally enrolled them because she felt the school curriculum was weak and she wanted to see them all study at advanced levels.\r\n\r\nSince beginning Kumon, she has seen a big difference and great improvement in their academic abilities. She notes the children have become more self-confident.\r\n\r\nOther activities the children enjoy include swimming, karate, water polo, and basketball.\r\n\r\nAdvice to someone considering Kumon: \"Don\'t hesitate. Start Kumon and you will see the difference, but be patient!\"\r\n\r\nTo read more success stories from centres all over North America, visit<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/Kumon\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.Facebook.com/Kumon</a>','Three Amazing Students','','publish','closed','closed','','test-testimonial-2','','','2015-09-22 14:17:21','2015-09-22 14:17:21','',0,'http://1pixeldesign.com/dev/wordpress2/?post_type=onepix_testimonial&#038;p=531',0,'onepix_testimonial','',0),(370,1,'2013-12-16 18:54:50','2013-12-16 18:54:50',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','370','','','2014-10-21 14:20:04','2014-10-21 14:20:04','',0,'http://ecbiz115.inmotionhosting.com/~mollys7/dev/wordpress2/?p=370',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(446,1,'2013-12-17 21:40:10','2013-12-17 21:40:10',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','446','','','2014-10-21 14:20:04','2014-10-21 14:20:04','',0,'http://ecbiz115.inmotionhosting.com/~mollys7/dev/wordpress2/?p=446',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(447,1,'2013-12-17 21:40:10','2013-12-17 21:40:10',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','447','','','2014-10-21 14:20:04','2014-10-21 14:20:04','',0,'http://ecbiz115.inmotionhosting.com/~mollys7/dev/wordpress2/?p=447',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1042,1,'2015-01-23 19:31:16','2015-01-23 19:31:16','','1060x579','','inherit','open','closed','','1060x579','','','2015-01-23 19:31:16','2015-01-23 19:31:16','',694,'http://1pixeldesign.com/dev/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/1060x579.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(568,1,'2014-06-14 14:49:50','2014-06-14 14:49:50','We celebrated our annual Awards ceremony for all our students on Tuesday, April 28, 2015, during our regular class hours of 3:30 to 7:00 p.m. The posters that summarize all awards may be seen on display in the study area at the centre.\r\n\r\nNow that autumn is here, we are completing the following summer contests:\r\n\r\n1) Summer Reading Challenge - the two students who read the most books in July and August, and write at least one paragraph on each book, in two different age categories (7 and under, 8 and up), will win the opportunity to purchase a book of their choice, up to a value of $30.\r\n\r\n2) Weekly Raffles - variety of prizes available in centre -now that we are settling into the fall routine, students have opportunities to submit raffle tickets for keeping up twice a week with getting homework checked and recorded on their trackers. Good study skills build strong self-learners.\r\n\r\n3) Level Up!Students who were enrolled during July, August and/or September will receive ballots for entry into a contest to win one of three $20 Chapters gift cards at the centre. Students earned additional ballots by moving on to a new level and by reaching or maintaining a spot on the Advanced Student Honour Roll.There will also be two Grand Prize Winners in our Toronto West branch who will each receive an iPad Mini provided by Kumon Canada!\r\n\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------','Gallery','','publish','open','closed','','showcase-page','','','2015-10-21 02:18:29','2015-10-21 02:18:29','',0,'http://1pixeldesign.com/dev/wordpress2/?page_id=568',0,'page','',0),(571,1,'2014-06-14 15:46:54','2014-06-14 15:46:54','','Skill1','','publish','closed','closed','','skill1','','','2014-08-27 20:45:35','2014-08-27 20:45:35','',0,'http://1pixeldesign.com/dev/wordpress2/?post_type=onepix_portfolio&#038;p=571',0,'onepix_portfolio','',0),(572,1,'2014-06-16 14:44:33','2014-06-16 14:44:33','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nam quis nulla nec neque eleifend consectetur in nec nisi. Vestibulum luctus justo ut lacus semper vestibulum. Nulla tempus erat sit amet dui interdum iaculis. Fusce quis sollicitudin lorem. Proin eu ipsum nec nisi sagittis vestibulum a sed metus. Aliquam adipiscing aliquet tellus. Integer porta arcu sit amet est pretium sit amet tristique orci dictum. . Suspendisse potenti. Aenean venenatis sagittis orci at fringilla. Etiam non dui at risus fringilla lacinia. Aenean auctor sapien sit amet quam rhoncus vehicula. Phasellus sem felis, lobortis ac accumsan eu, rutrum vel ante. Cras sed mi vel lorem porttitor adipiscing. Integer enim sem, ultricies quis adipiscing id, ullamcorper sit amet justo. Aenean eg