:11','2015-09-22 13:58:11','',531,'http://kumonofhamiltonwestend.ca/531-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1128,1,'2015-06-09 21:48:31','2015-06-09 21:48:31',' ','','','publish','open','closed','','1128','','','2015-09-24 00:45:04','2015-09-24 00:45:04','',0,'http://kumonofhamiltonwestend.ca/?p=1128',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1563,1,'2015-09-23 13:23:14','2015-09-23 13:23:14','<strong>February:</strong>\r\n\r\nMy recent business trip to Malaysia - blogged here:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://kumonofhamiltonwestend.wordpress.com/2016/02/01/malaysia/\">https://kumonofhamiltonwestend.wordpress.com/2016/02/01/malaysia/</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>January:</strong>\r\n\r\nGet the latest details about our rescheduled Open House in March, scheduling progress updates about your child, and how to maximize your referral bonuses when you encourage your friends to join Kumon.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/bOF1Cr\">http://eepurl.com/bOF1Cr</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table class=\"templateContainer\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id=\"templateBody\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<table class=\"mcnTextBlock\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<table class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\" border=\"0\" width=\"600\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mcnTextContent\" valign=\"top\"><strong>Sailing Into September Newsletter 2015</strong><a href=\"http://kumonofhamiltonwestend.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Boys-dive-into-the-Medite-008.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1574\" src=\"http://kumonofhamiltonwestend.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Boys-dive-into-the-Medite-008.jpg\" alt=\"Boys dive into the Mediterranean from Cleopatra\'s Rock, on the Egyptian coast 500km north of Cairo.\" width=\"460\" height=\"276\" /></a>Has September felt like diving into the unknown ocean rather than sailing into the sunset? Autumn can be a very challenging season, especially for families with lots of activities on their plate.\r\n\r\nPerhaps <strong>checking your child\'s homework</strong> feels like one extra challenging item? Consider:\r\n\r\n1) It takes as little as<strong> 2-5 minutes per day.</strong>\r\n2) It can make the difference between your child stalling in Kumon because the same mistakes are repeated every day (or worse, worksheets are being skipped or completed carelessly), or your child progressing smoothly and beautifully.\r\n3) Without it, your child can get the impression that Kumon is not really important to you. After all, your child must do 20 minutes or more of work 7 days a week on Kumon. If you do not even give 2 minutes a day to support your child\'s work, it doesn\'t look like you value their efforts.\r\n4) Your child gets<strong> instant positive feedback</strong> when the work is perfect, or close to perfect. How great is that for a warm glow and motivation to keep doing a good job?\r\n5) Our <strong>weekly raffle draws</strong> are now based on all homework being checked and entered on the homework tracker. If you don\'t check the homework, your child misses out on those fun draws.\r\n\r\nOur <strong>answer books</strong> make checking work very quick and easy. If you need an answer book or any guidance with how to do it and correctly enter results on the homework tracker, simply ask Holly at the reception desk the next time you are at Kumon. She will be more than happy to assist you.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class=\"mcnTextBlock\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<table class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\" border=\"0\" width=\"600\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mcnTextContent\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<h1>LevelUp Ballots</h1>\r\nDepending on how many months your children have been in the program, whether they are doing both math and reading, whether they have just attained a new Advanced Honour Roll level, or how many levels they have completed in the past three months, they may receive between one and 10 or more ballots to possibly win a Chapters gift card.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id=\"templateColumns\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<table class=\"columnWrapper\" border=\"0\" width=\"300\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"columnContainer\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<table class=\"mcnTextBlock\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<table class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\" border=\"0\" width=\"300\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mcnTextContent\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-family: georgia, times, \'times new roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-family: georgia, times, \'times new roman\', serif;\"><strong><u>Summer Reading Challenge</u></strong></span></span>Please return your book summaries as soon as possible so we may choose the winners. Thank you so much for your help.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class=\"columnWrapper\" border=\"0\" width=\"300\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"columnContainer\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<table class=\"mcnImageCardBlock\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody class=\"mcnImageCardBlockOuter\">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mcnImageCardBlockInner\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<table class=\"mcnImageCardBottomContent\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mcnImageCardBottomImageContent\" align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"mcnImage\" src=\"https://gallery.mailchimp.com/38f3a34240ea7b0c86f7382a7/images/9c001d9f-0df4-4935-b2fe-3ea0aa09d988.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"264\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mcnTextContent\" valign=\"top\" width=\"246\">If you are new, you have not yet experienced one of our very motivating and enjoyable Annual Awards Classes. Our next awards day is in April, so let\'s work hard over the fall and winter and see how advanced you can become - can you reach the first Advanced Honour Roll level in time?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','News','','publish','open','closed','','news','','','2016-02-01 22:46:40','2016-02-01 22:46:40','',0,'http://kumonofhamiltonwestend.ca/?page_id=1563',0,'page','',0),(964,1,'2015-09-23 13:17:45','2015-09-23 13:17:45','<h3>Kumon of Hamilton West End</h3>\n[circleimage has_hovericon=false hovericon=fa-chevron-circle-right class=\"alignright\" imgurl=http://kumonofhamiltonwestend.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/001-e1436885039303.jpg] Centre Director and Instructor, Nicole Smith, has 20 years experience running Kumon centres in Montreal and Ontario, working in both French and English. She has through her Kumon centres helped many hundreds of students over these years develop in their math, English, and learning skills, including her own three children, all of whom are successfully pursuing careers and university studies in Montreal.\n\nOur staff:\n\n1) Our receptionist, Holly Fraser, has worked the longest of all the staff at the centre, and has become very knowledgeable about the Kumon programs and how best to help children get a good start and make excellent progress at the centre.\n\