or skills, neatness of presentation, concentration/focus and the facility to study steadily instead of being constantly distracted, and so on.\r\n\r\nIn 5A through 3A of Reading and 4A and early 3A of Math, students prepare for the big transition to the main study area of Kumon where they will be developing more and more independent study skills at a pace comfortable for each child.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Early Learners','','inherit','open','closed','','1515-revision-v1','','','2015-07-14 17:11:53','2015-07-14 17:11:53','',1515,'http://kumonofhamiltonwestend.ca/1515-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1524,1,'2015-08-26 01:03:48','2015-08-26 01:03:48','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nam quis nulla nec neque eleifend consectetur in nec nisi. Vestibulum luctus justo ut lacus semper vestibulum. Nulla tempus erat sit amet dui interdum iaculis.','Study Area','','inherit','open','closed','','1069-autosave-v1','','','2015-08-26 01:03:48','2015-08-26 01:03:48','',1069,'http://kumonofhamiltonwestend.ca/1069-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1527,1,'2015-08-26 01:10:50','2015-08-26 01:10:50','','G by 5 Award','','publish','closed','closed','','g-by-5-award','','','2015-08-26 01:10:50','2015-08-26 01:10:50','',0,'http://kumonofhamiltonwestend.ca/?post_type=onepix_showcase&#038;p=1527',0,'onepix_showcase','',0),(1528,1,'2015-08-26 01:10:20','2015-08-26 01:10:20','','g by 5 award','','inherit','open','closed','','g-by-5-award','','','2015-08-26 01:10:20','2015-08-26 01:10:20','',1527,'http://kumonofhamiltonwestend.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/g-by-5-award.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1529,1,'2015-08-26 01:11:27','2015-08-26 01:11:27','','Summer Photo Contest 2015','','publish','closed','closed','','summer-photo-contest-2015','','','2015-08-26 01:11:27','2015-08-26 01:11:27','',0,'http://kumonofhamiltonwestend.ca/?post_type=onepix_showcase&#038;p=1529',0,'onepix_showcase','',0),(1530,1,'2015-08-26 01:11:19','2015-08-26 01:11:19','','kumon summer photo co